item.title: CVE-2022-4678|2024-08-03T01:48:39.494Z -- unknown -- templatesnext%20toolkit
item.description: The TemplatesNext ToolKit WordPress plugin before 3.2.8 does not validate and escape some of its shortcode attributes before outputting them back in a page/post where the shortcode is embed, which could allow users with the contributor role and above to perform Stored Cross-Site Scripting attacks.
